Standard library:.text:
mark the Stream and Genlex modules as deprecated, in preparation
  for a future removal.  These modules (without deprecation alert)
  are now provided by the camlp-streams library.

Other libraries (highlights):.text:
update documentation of the threads library;
  deprecate Thread.kill, Thread.wait_read, Thread.wait_write,
  and the whole ThreadUnix module.

Type system.text:
unique names for weak type variables
    # ref [];;
    - : '_weak1 list ref = {contents = []}

Code generation and optimizations:.text:
Optimize performance of record update:
  no more performance cliff when { foo with t1 = ..; t2 = ...; ... }
  hits 6 updated fields

Language features:.text:
Syntax shortcut for putting a type annotation on a record field:
  { f1 : typ = e } is sugar for { f1 = (e : typ) }
  { f1 : typ } is sugar for { f1 = (f1 : typ) }
